games.comment: Victor Cruz to score. Manning finished 16-of-23 for 254 yards and 4 touchdowns. Two were to Cruz, 1 went to Bradshaw, and the other was thrown to

Victor Cruz were targeted a ton as well, which isn't a surprise considering that Manning threw the ball 63 times. Shepard (7-61) hauled in Manning's sole touchdown, while Cruz caught 8 balls for 84 yards.    The Giants ran better than expected once again, thanks in part to Pugh's return.
